msgid "# triton.language.swizzle2d"
msgstr "# triton.language.swizzle2d"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:4
msgid "简介：**将一个大小为 size_i × size_j 的行优先矩阵的索引，按每 size_g 行一组，分别转换为列优先矩阵的索引。**。"
msgstr "Introduction: **Convert the index of a row-major matrix of size size_i × size_j, grouped every size_g rows, into the index of a column-major matrix.**"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.swizzle2d(i, j, size_i, size_j, size_g)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `i`        | `tensor`          | index索引值 ，最大值为size(i)-1                                                     |\n"
"| `j`        | `tensor`          | index索引值 ，最大值为size(j)-1                                                     |\n"
"| `size_i`        | `int`          | 整型，表示索引值i的长度                                                     |\n"
"| `size_j`        | `int`          | 整型，表示索引值j的长度                                                          |\n"
"| `size_g`        | `int`          | 整型                                                      |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type     | Description                                                  |\n"
"| --------- | -------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| `i`       | `tensor` | Index value, maximum is `size(i)-1`                          |\n"
"| `j`       | `tensor` | Index value, maximum is `size(j)-1`                          |\n"
"| `size_i`  | `int`    | Integer, indicating the length of index value i              |\n"
"| `size_j`  | `int`    | Integer, indicating the length of index value j              |\n"
"| `size_g`  | `int`    | Integer                                                      |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`out0, out1`：同i, j shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`out0, out1`: Tensors with the same shape as i, j\n"

