#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:34
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:36
msgid "以下示例将行优先矩阵的索引按每 `size_g` 行一组转换为列优先矩阵的索引："
msgstr "The following example converts row-major matrix indices into column-major matrix indices in groups of `size_g` rows each:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/swizzle2d.md:38
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def fn_npu_(out0, out1, XB: tl.constexpr, YB: tl.constexpr, ZB: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    i = tl.arange(0, XB)[:, None]\n"
"    j = tl.arange(0, YB)[None, :]\n"
"    ij = i * YB + j\n"
"    xx, yy = tl.swizzle2d(i, j, size_i=XB, size_j=YB, size_g=ZB)\n"
"\n"
"    ptr = tl.load(out0)\n"
"    xx = tl.cast(xx, dtype=ptr.dtype)\n"
"    yy = tl.cast(yy, dtype=ptr.dtype)\n"
"    tl.store(out0 + ij, xx)\n"
"    tl.store(out1 + ij, yy)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

